            "id": "65cb5d48f7c541acb2508",
            "questionText": "A star with an initial mass of $!$30$!$ solar masses undergoes stellar evolution. After spending several million years on the main sequence, it exhausts the hydrogen fuel in its core and eventually undergoes a supernova explosion. Suppose that after the supernova, the remnant core collapses to form a black hole. If the black hole's mass is determined to be $!$8$!$ solar masses and $!$2$!$ solar masses worth of energy is released, what is the proportion of the mass that the black hole retained relative to the mass of the released energy?",
            "imageText": "",
            "steps": [
                {
                    "id": "dc6a468227414bfbaba52",
                    "stepText": "Let's compare the retained mass with the released energy, we need to form a ratio. Which mathematical operation would correctly allow you to form a ratio of the retained mass to the released mass equivalent?",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        ""
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "",
                    "stepConcepts": [],
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$\\frac{\\text{Retained Mass}}{\\text{Released Energy Mass}}$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": true
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$\\text{Retained Mass} \\times \\text{Released Energy Mass}$!$ (Multiplication)",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$\\text{Retained Mass} - \\text{Released Energy Mass}$!$ (Subtraction)",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$\\text{Retained Mass} + \\text{Released Energy Mass}$!$ (Addition)",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "e494dd6d42ad4881bec29",
